plot: After a little white lie about losing her virginity gets out, a clean cut high school girl sees her life paralleling Hester Prynne's in &"The Scarlet Letter,&" which she is currently studying in school - until she decides to use the rumor mill to advance her social and financial standing.   Written by  Sony Pictures
